in">Maya Da-Rin</a></dt><dd>Brazil</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/cheryl-dunye">Cheryl Dunye</a></dt><dd></dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/oriol-estrada">Oriol Estrada</a></dt><dd>Spain/Dominican Republic</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/daniel-goldhaber">Daniel Goldhaber</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/helen-grace">Helen Grace</a></dt><dd>Australia</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/robert-greene">Robert Greene</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/luca-guadagnino">Luca Guadagnino</a></dt><dd>Italy</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/joanna-hogg">Joanna Hogg</a></dt><dd>UK</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/dea-kulumbegashvili">Dea Kulumbegashvili</a></dt><dd>Georgia</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/karyn-kusama">Karyn Kusama</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/joe-christine-lawlor-molloy">Joe Lawlor &amp; Christine Molloy</a></dt><dd>Ireland</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/jackie-lentzou">Jackie Lentzou</a></dt><dd>Greece</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/david-lowery">David Lowery</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/manuela-martelli">Manuela Martelli</a></dt><dd>Chile</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/adam-mckay">Adam McKay</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/kleber-mendonca-filho">Kleber Mendonça Filho</a></dt><dd>Brazil</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/nina-menkes">Nina Menkes</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-f